2Lines is a personal fertility tracking and pregnancy journey application. It provides cycle tracking, ovulation predictions, pregnancy monitoring, contraction timing, birth planning, and keepsake creation features.

## Subscriptions and Payments

### Free Tier

The free version of 2Lines includes basic journey tracking, cycle logging, daily symptom tracking, and limited photo/audio storage. Free accounts display advertisements powered by Google AdMob.

### 2Lines+ Subscriptions

2Lines+ is available as a Monthly subscription ($3.99/month), Annual subscription ($29.99/year), or Lifetime purchase ($49.99 one-time).

**Payment:** Payment is charged to your Apple ID account at confirmation of purchase.

**Auto-Renewal:** Monthly and Annual subscriptions automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current billing period. Your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period at the same price.

**Lifetime Purchase:** The Lifetime plan is a one-time, non-recurring purchase that grants permanent access to all 2Lines+ features.

**Managing Subscriptions:** You can manage or cancel your subscription at any time through your Apple ID Settings > Subscriptions.

**Free Trial:** If a free trial is offered, the unused portion of the trial is forfeited upon purchasing a subscription.

**Refunds:** Refunds are handled by Apple in accordance with their refund policies. To request a refund, visit reportaproblem.apple.com.

### Ad-Free Experience

All 2Lines+ subscribers (Monthly, Annual, or Lifetime) receive an ad-free experience. If a subscription lapses or is canceled, advertisements will resume.

## Medical Disclaimer

**2Lines is not a medical device and does not provide medical advice.**

The fertility predictions, ovulation estimates, and health tracking features in 2Lines are based on user-entered data and published scientific methods (including the Symptothermal Method, Billings Ovulation Method, and standard cycle analysis). These predictions are estimates only and should not be relied upon as a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.

2Lines does not diagnose medical conditions, predict pregnancy outcomes, or replace consultation with a qualified healthcare provider. Always seek the advice of your physician or other qualified health provider with any questions regarding a medical condition or reproductive health.

The contraction timer and 5-1-1 rule analysis are informational tools only. Always contact your healthcare provider or go to the hospital if you believe you are in labor or experiencing a medical emergency.

